<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>所有文章 - 毕少侠</title><link>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/</link><description>Talk is cheap. Show me the code.</description><generator>Hugo 0.147.5 &amp; FixIt v0.3.20</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>geekswg@qq.com (geekswg)</managingEditor><webMaster>geekswg@qq.com (geekswg)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 May 2025 19:43:26 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>给你的 Markdown 挑挑刺</title><link>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/markdownlint/</link><pubDate>Wed, 11 Oct 2023 14:26:48 +0800</pubDate><author>geekswg@qq.com (geekswg)</author><guid>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/markdownlint/</guid><category domain="https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/categories/%E8%BD%AC%E8%BD%BD/">转载</category><description>&lt;p>会写 Markdown 的人很多，但写得好 Markdown 的人却很少。有没有什么工具能充当「秘书」，检查文件中的 Markdown 语法和风格，并且提出解决方案、自动修复问题，甚至自动补齐中英文之间的「盘古之白」呢？本文介绍的 Markdown 语法检查器就能做到。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>中文翻译的常见问题</title><link>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/translation-guide/</link><pubDate>Fri, 15 Sep 2023 11:07:56 +0800</pubDate><author>geekswg@qq.com (geekswg)</author><guid>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/translation-guide/</guid><category domain="https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/categories/%E8%BD%AC%E8%BD%BD/">转载</category><category domain="https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/categories/%E7%BF%BB%E8%AF%91/">翻译</category><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>以下内容截取自 &lt;a href="https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/docs/zh-cn/translation-guide.md"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">针对 MDN 文档的本地化指南&lt;/a> 的中文翻译的常见问题小节。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>其中翻译的规范也是中文写作的规范，更多详见之前写的 &lt;a href="https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/document-style-guide/">中文技术文档的写作规范&lt;/a>。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>为保证简体中文文档格式的一致性，翻译指南列出了部分规范。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>中文技术文档的写作规范</title><link>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/document-style-guide/</link><pubDate>Sat, 04 Feb 2023 16:04:42 +0800</pubDate><author>geekswg@qq.com (geekswg)</author><guid>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/document-style-guide/</guid><category domain="https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/categories/%E8%BD%AC%E8%BD%BD/">转载</category><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>以下参考来源：阮一峰的 &lt;a href="https://github.com/ruanyf/document-style-guide"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">中文技术文档的写作规范&lt;/a>&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;p>英语世界里，文档非常受重视，许多公司和组织都有自己的文档规范，清楚地规定写作要求，比如&lt;a href="https://www.microsoftpressstore.com/store/microsoft-manual-of-style-9780735648715"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">微软&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="http://styleguide.mailchimp.com/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">MailChimp&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://help.apple.com/asg/mac/2013/ASG_2013.pdf"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Apple&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B003P8QDFU/ref=dp-kindle-redirect?_encoding=UTF8&amp;amp;btkr=1"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Yahoo&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://docs.docker.com/opensource/doc-style/"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">docker&lt;/a>、&lt;a href="https://struts.apache.org/docs/documentation-style-guide.html"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">Struts&lt;/a> 等等（维基百科有一份完整的&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_style_guides"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">清单&lt;/a>）。&lt;a href="https://github.com/ruanyf/document-style-guide/blob/master/docs/reference.md"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">中文的&lt;/a>也有不少，但都不令人满意，要么太简单，要么不太适用。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对于开发者来说，在工作中也需要适当地产出一些技术文档，但是很多人都不知道怎么写文档，都是凭着感觉写。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>对于开发的系统、软件而言，系统用词的准确性和统一性也显得十分重要。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>参考上面的规范，于是有了下面一份中文技术文档的写作规范。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Hello World</title><link>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/hello-world/</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 Sep 2022 17:06:11 +0800</pubDate><author>geekswg@qq.com (geekswg)</author><guid>https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/posts/hello-world/</guid><category domain="https://geekswg.js.cool/blog-fixit-go/categories/hello/">Hello</category><description>&lt;p>Welcome to Hugo FixIt! This is your very first post.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>